Credits
-------

-  `django-import-export <https://github.com/django-import-export/django-import-export>`__
   - Pieces of the admin code are heavily inspired by this library, it
   also includes the modules for formats and temporary storage.
-  `tablib <https://github.com/jazzband/tablib>`__ - Enables us to load
   data from several data formats.

